snippet.title: Rainbow Six Quarantine: E3 2019 Official Teaser | Ubisoft
snippet.description:
Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Quarantine™ is a 3-player squad-based survival FPS being developed by an entirely new team at Ubisoft Montreal. 

The Rainbow Six operators will face off against a mysterious threat infecting human hosts and their surroundings.  

Prepare to launch into tense, chaotic, and totally unpredictable missions as you and your squad risk everything every time you step into quarantine. 

Coming early 2020 on PS4, Xbox One, PC.
